==Facilities==
*'''[[Hydra Headquarters]]''': Zola conducted his science experiments from [[Hydra]]'s headquarters, and housed his inventions there.
*'''[[Hydra Base Camp C3]]''': Zola and [[Johann Schmidt]] used a [[Hydra]] facility in [[Austria]] and forced prisoners to build weapons there. Zola and Schmidt were in the facility when [[Steve Rogers|Captain America]] arrived, so they destroyed the facility in an attempt to. Although Schmidt at first was not going to allow Zola to leave the facility, but eventually allowed Zola to escape in his [[Johann Schmidt's Coupe|coupe]].
*'''[[Camp Lehigh]]''': Zola was recruited to [[S.H.I.E.L.D.]] and worked with [[Howard Stark]] in Camp Lehigh. When he died, his mind was uploaded to computers and kept in the base. He was confronted in Lehigh by [[Steve Rogers]] and [[Natasha Romanoff]], where he revealed that [[Hydra]] had [[Hydra Uprising|infiltrated]] S.H.I.E.L.D., and then destroyed the facility.

